reviewText: Not a day goes by with out my son asking to watch this repeatedly. Great DVD

As a homeschooling mom and mother of four I have to say that this video is great for all ages.  My 2, 4, and 6 year old all enjoy watching this dvd and can learn something from it.  You can also play the card game by going to the website--an extra special feature my kids love.  Thanks Leap Frog!!

These teach to small children in a way that a person may never be able to get through to them. I have every Leap Frog DVD for my Kindergarten classroom and they get better with every single one! This DVD teaches rhyming, storytelling, and word building just to name a few things.
Great for my children. My son who is now in Kindergarten can learn to read in a fun way.

My kids have truly been growing up with all the Leapfrog series, and the result is that they are more academically advanced than most of the kids their ages. Totally worth the money spent on buying these series because it both educational and fun. This DVD is perfect for kindergarteners who have just begun learning to write and putting their thoughts together.

reviewed from my children

Very educational movies. My 5 year old and 2 year old have learned so much from watching these leapfrog movies. Within a week or so they could tell me all the letter sounds. Leapfrog makes it very easy to remember what sounds the letter makes by making them into charters. We bought more movies.
Best sound alphabet movie I've seen!  My kids love this fun story and song.  I've told many people about this and all have been happy. Highly Recommend. Great for car rides.
